\begin_layout Subsection
Gene matrix (GMX)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
GMX file format is a simple tab delimited file to provide gene sets.
 Each column describes a gene set, the first row indicates the name of the
 gene set and the second row the description (you can leave description
 empty).
 
\end_layout

